S'Access easy-to-use mortgage calculators and shop for real-time mortgage rates on the spot in this elegantly designed Zillow Mortgage Marketplace Android App, brought to you by the makers of the most popular platform of mobile real estate applications.*Calculate how much home you can afford, what your mortgage payment will be and whether it makes sense to refinance. Plus, receive personalized loan quotes from rated and reviewed lenders. You contact them when you\xe2\x80\x99re ready.MAIN FEATURES:Mortgage CalculatorsAffordability calculator:  Calculate the home price you can afford and money left over after your home loan payment.  Ideal for renters, or first time home buyers.Payment calculator: See your estimated monthly mortgage payment and how it breaks down into principal, interest, taxes and mortgage insurance.  Re-adjust figures for different home price, down-payment and rate scenarios.Refinance calculator: Estimate how much money you could save if you refinance. Includes breakeven point and savings over the life of the loan. Each home loan calculator includes: Interactive sliders and data input fields, cool, data-generated charts, simple and advanced calculator views, and fields pre-filled with latest rates and cost estimates. Mortgage Rate Shopping Three steps to get low purchase or refinance rates from trusted lenders on Zillow Mortgage Marketplace: 1) Create a custom loan request: Enter details about the loan you want, your budget and estimated credit score.  Do this anonymously \xe2\x80\x93 no need to enter personal contact info. 2) Lenders respond to request:Lenders instantly return loan quotes with details on the monthly payment, interest rate and lender fees.  3) Borrowers decide: Borrowers review lender ratings and reviews and compare loan quotes. Borrowers then contact a lender they like \xe2\x80\x93 instantly. Zillow\xe2\x80\x99s mortgage shopping experience gives borrowers choice \xe2\x80\x93 on average borrowers receive 18 custom quotes for a purchase or refinance mortgage loan request \xe2\x80\x93 and borrowers can select from a broad set of product options including an FHA loan or a VA loan.Interactive Rate Graphs - Customize graphs of interest rates by time span, loan program and geography -Get a snapshot of current mortgage rates today, with interest rates updated in real time- View intraday changes of mortgage interest rates, or graph rates by day, week, month, 3 months, 1-year, and 2-year time  frames - Choose from 30 year fixed mortgage rates, 15 year mortgage rates, and 5/1 ARM - Includes state and national rate trends All results can be shared via email, text message, or Twitter.*Zillow Internal, 2012'
